title: 'Worth the cost'

body: 'Good and in the label it has mentioned that its an anti rust stainless steel but its not so. Think before you buy. Sharpness is good.'

title: It's not strong at all
body: 'They are very thin and not strong at all. You will have hard time to open anything even a bit strong. Like for example packages.'

title: 'Good product but rusts if not cared properly'
body: 'Good product. Nice shape and sharpness. But if using in kitchen or anywhere with proximity of water extra care should be taken to avoid rust. The one which i am using in kitchen got rust within a month. But after cleaning and applying some oil it was cleared.'

title: 'Good set of scissors'
body: 'Good set of scissors . Value for money. Cuts a variety of materials even metal. Quite sturdy.'
